The paper discusses the application of data mining methods, specifically association rule mining, and the use of information cartography for visualizing the results. This falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with data mining (cs.DM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. The use of visualization and user interaction also suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
